@startuml
actor User
participant "UserProgressController" as C
participant "UserProgressService" as S
participant "UserProgressRepository" as R

User -> C: GET /progress/leaderboard
C -> S: getLeaderboard()
S -> R: getLeaderboard() [custom query]
R --> S: List<Object[]> (userId, username, totalPoints)
S -> S: convert to LeaderboardEntryDto
S --> C: List<LeaderboardEntryDto>
C --> User: 200 OK + leaderboard
@enduml